"""
AI-READI Dataset Loader Template for Sakana AI-Scientist-v2

Data is available at: ../input/ relative to agent working directory (no Data_Read subfolder).

Dataset: AI-READI mini v1.0.0 - Multi-modal diabetes study
100 participants, 4 study groups:
  - healthy
  - pre_diabetes_lifestyle_controlled
  - oral_medication_and_or_non_insulin_injectable_medication_controlled
  - insulin_dependent

Available modalities (see participants.tsv boolean flags):
  - cardiac_ecg         : 12-lead ECG, Philips TC30, 500 Hz, WFDB format (.hea + .dat)
  - clinical_data       : OMOP CDM CSVs (measurement, person, observation, condition_occurrence, ...)
  - environment         : Leelab Anura environmental sensor JSON
  - retinal_flio        : Retinal FLIO DICOM
  - retinal_oct         : Retinal OCT DICOM (Topcon Maestro2, Topcon Triton, Zeiss Cirrus)
  - retinal_octa        : Retinal OCTA DICOM (enface, flow_cube, segmentation)
  - retinal_photography : Retinal CFP/FAF/IR DICOM (multiple devices)
  - wearable_blood_glucose : Dexcom G6 CGM JSON (OpenMHealth schema)
"""

